.SS "\s-1FILES\s0"
.IX Subsection "FILES"
Locations for the \fIwinoptions\fR file are as follows:
.PP
.Vb 5
\& $ICEWM_PRIVCFG/winoptions
\& $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/icewm/winoptions
